name: Nightmare on My Street
description:
FEAR4HEN. I had a dream where I was being attacked by Nazis and Jason (he rose out of the water and everything).  Then I remember running and I see Freddy.  And he sees me and points at me with his claw.  So I turn around and start running the other way (back towards Jason and the Nazis).  Then in a typical movie fashion, I trip and fall.  I look back and Freddy is leaning down towards me with he claw finger.  He pushes it into my chest.  Then I wake up feeling a stinging feeling in my chest.  That was right after the Jason Vs Freddy movie came out. 
Enjoy.  www.theguidingrock.com
